title: Togainu no Chi Volume 5
description: Akira battles a Line-addicted Takeru, who seems to be energized to an insane, superhuman level. Although Takeru seems to have the upper hand, he then licks some blood dripping down Akira's face, and then begins to suffer from convulsions - apparently an incompatibility disorder to Line!
author: Suguro Chayamachi
